mann]]\n|-\n|align=center|34\n|align=right|12 May 2002\n|[[Aerus Electrolux USA Championship]]\n|\u221217 (65-72-70-64=271)\n|1 stroke\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Pat Hurst]]\n|-\n|align=center|35\n|align=right|2 Jun 2002\n|[[Kellogg-Keebler Classic]]\n|\u221221 (63-67-65=195)\n|11 strokes\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Michele Redman]] <br> {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Mhairi McKay]] <br> {{flagicon|USA}} [[Danielle Ammaccapane]]\n|-\n|align=center|36\n|align=right|15 Jun 2002\n|[[Evian Masters]]\n|\u221219 (68-67-65-69=269)\n|4 strokes\n|{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Maria Hjorth]] <br> {{flagicon|KOR}} [[Mi Hyun Kim]]\n|-\n|align=center|37\n|align=right|30 Jun 2002\n|[[ShopRite LPGA Classic]]\n|\u221212 (68-67-66=201)\n|3 strokes\n|{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Carin Koch]] <br> {{flagicon|USA}} [[Kate Golden]]\n|-\n|align=center|38\n|align=right|8 Sep 2002\n|[[Williams Championship]]\n|\u221211 (68-66-65=199)\n|4 strokes\n|{{flagicon|CAN}} [[Lorie Kane]]\n|-\n|align=center|39\n|align=right|15 Sep 2002\n|[[Safeway Classic]]\n|\u221217 (69-62-68=199)\n|1 stroke\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Kate Golden]]\n|-\n|align=center|40\n|align=right|6 Oct 2002\n|[[Samsung World Championship]]\n|\u221222 (66-67-68-65=266)\n|6 strokes\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Cristie Kerr]]\n|-\n|align=center|41\n|align=right|10 Nov 2002\n|[[Mizuno Classic]]\n|\u221215 (69-65-67=201)\n|2 strokes\n|{{flagicon|KOR}} [[Grace Park (golfer)|Grace Park]]\n|-\n|align=center|42\n|align=right|24 Nov 2002\n|[[ADT Championship]]\n|\u221213 (67-70-70-68=275)\n|3 strokes\n|{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Rachel Teske]]\n|-\n|align=center|43\n|align=right|6 Apr [[2003 LPGA Tour|2003]]\n|[[The Office Depot Championship]]\n|\u22125 (68-72-71=211)\n|4 strokes\n|{{flagicon|KOR}} [[Se Ri Pak]] <br> {{flagicon|USA}} [[Pat Hurst]] <br> {{flagicon|USA}} [[Heather Bowie]]\n|-\n|align=center|44\n|align=right|1 Jun 2003\n|[[Kellogg-Keebler Classic]]\n|\u221217 (62-66-71=199)\n|3 strokes\n|{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Mhairi McKay]]\n|- style=\"background:#e5d1cb;\"\n|align=center|45\n|align=right|8 J